{
  "stem": "8072.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was still-- I was doing it little bit at that time, trying to take it off.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was this one man there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was also a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says to me, Morrie, let me take a-- let me look at it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I showed it to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he just ripped it off, which was better, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He just ripped it off all at once.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, I don't remember exactly how, but when he ripped it off, that, the German or something, he saw it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he took me in again to their dispensary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he a put a little cream on and re-bandaged it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it healed a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a-- he wasn't an SS man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a civilian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was doing-- he was in charge-- he was an engineer in charge of the work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was a human being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, he didn't like what, what was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was a human being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, I-- he wasn't afraid to do this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't dangerous for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, the SS weren't-- the SS weren't in charge of him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a civilian engineer and things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If they would've caught him, I don't think they would do anything to him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They could have said, don't do this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he wasn't-- it wasn't any danger to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This camp that you mentioned, Dachau, but a little bit away from Dachau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It did, but I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell you another thing that I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
